  "description": "Is the bot making things up? Watches the LLM gateway for hedging phrases (\"I think\", \"approximately\") and explicit hallucination signals. The hallucination alert fires when the 15m rate is \u22652\u00d7 the trailing 4h baseline. Hover the \u2139 icon on any panel for what each number means.",
